data.description: NEW ROOF 2021. No HOA & No Flood Zone. NW Bradenton, West side of Manatee Ave. A few streets from the boat ramp. On a .30 acre lot with large shade trees & a large backyard, perfect for a future detached office or pool. The rooms are generous in size. The Kitchen has been completely updated, Nolte cabinets, gray quartz countertops with a large granite top island, Jen-Air appliances, large single sink. Open plan. Porcelain wood planks in the main area with built in Bahamas style shutters in the living room. Central AC - 2012; Water Heater - 2014. Manatee High, King Middle district.
data.whatILove:
Location! It’s close to the beach & downtown. Great school district, and super easy access to the boat ramp. No HOA. 
NEW ROOF IN 2021!
